        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1710268066" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14868255574114219866">I found this old book in an antique shop and it was a real treat. It tells the story of Lillian who is slowly dying and how she leaves a hospital in search of living out her final days in full. She meets Clerfayt, a race car driver. Essentially they each live for the moment and fall in love. We are all living an instant at a time, who know if we have a long life and does the future extend only to the next breath we each take. Who knows? </span>

          </span>
        </div>


